articles.title: Australian woman, 95, dies after police shoot her with stun gun - Honolulu Star-Advertiser
articles.description: CANBERRA, Australia >> A 95-year-old Australian woman died Wednesday, a week after a police officer shot her with a stun gun in a nursing home as she moved toward him using a walker and carrying a steak knife, in a tragedy that has outraged many Australians.
